        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/fbc32d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-02-01T17:25:59.940Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Updated to 7.71.2 and the same problem is still there. I am beginning to think that either Signal is not aware of the problem OR they do not see this as a problem. Could it be that they did this on purpose? Is this just the new behavior?</p>\n<p>I am thinking no because I have friends with iPhones and on that platform it works correctly, that is to say that it works the way it used to work for me. Everyone I know that has android is experiencing the same bug that I am though.</p>\n<p>Any hope for this being fixed?</p>",
