        "cooked": "<p>I don\u2019t think it\u2019s supposed to be a new behaviour since <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/alex-signal\">@alex-signal</a>  mentioned fixing it. It also doesn\u2019t happen on any of my Android devices.</p>",
