        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/fbc32d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-02-03T22:38:32.842Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Interesting. I wonder what I have different on my Android. I wonder if I uninstall and reinstall it if that would help? My friends phone has the same issue and is also android. I emailed tech support to make sure that they were aware of the issue. They responded with some questions for me which I answered but I have not heard back from them yet.</p>\n<p>I also pointed them to this topic, if it helps.</p>",
